bits: Best deeds are consistent, even if small","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 14, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTake up good deeds only as much as you are able, for the best deeds are those done regularly even if they are few.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 8600 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21403,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/12\/28\/wahb-moderation-balance-middle-ground\/","url_meta":{"origin":27250,"position":3},"title":"Wahb on Moderation: Everything has balance, seek the middle ground","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 28, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Wahb ibn Munnabih, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cVerily, everything has two ends and a middle. If you hold one of the ends, the other will be skewed. If you hold the middle, the two ends will be balanced. You must seek the middle ground\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3935,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/01\/moderation-good-habits\/","url_meta":{"origin":27250,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Moderation: Allah loves small good habits, not burning out","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO people, you must only perform deeds you are capable of doing. By Allah, Allah will not give up on you unless you give up. Verily, the most beloved deeds to Allah are those performed regularly, even\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8636,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/22\/shir-poetry-good-evil\/","url_meta":{"origin":27250,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Shi&#8217;r: Poetry is used for good or evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPoetry is in the same position as speech. The beautiful among it is like beautiful words, and the ugly among it is like ugly words.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 862 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/27250","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-